commit.message:
h8300-protos.h: Replace emit_a_shift with output_a_shift.

	* config/h8300/h8300-protos.h: Replace emit_a_shift with
	output_a_shift.
	* config/h8300/h8300.c: Likewise.
	* config/h8300/h8300.md: Likewise.

From-SVN: r48935

+	* config/h8300/h8300.c: Likewise.
